{"tid":1457182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"散水唔散水?","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:57.000Z","uid":238027,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcf33483382a20db6e54b57894d0d2c9e25f68e","tid":1457182,"uid":238027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:21:29.000Z","msg":"首先嚟個利申：我係5點半左右走咗嘅，雖然冇呼籲人走不過都姑且叫我散水撚is fine<br />\n<br />\n有好多人話啲機重新升降喇乜乜柒柒；大佬你嗰啲Arrival就由佢啦，至少6點打後Departure嘅全部cancel曬先啦。Cancel咗嘅航班幾日唔會臨時話飛返，你ok啲旅客都唔ok啦，酒店門口接送咩？<br />\n<br />\n其實癱瘓機場呢個目標已經做到，你可能會唔認同，咁請問你覺得要坐到幾時先真係叫可以走呢？輪更制喺冇大台冇龍頭情況之下根本冇可能做到。既然犬方已經出動咗速龍同旗手，幾時進攻係佢地話事；喺少人嘅時候俾佢地嚟個突擊咁樣又少幾個手足真係有意思咩?<br />\n<br />\n既然一開始話Be Water，要打游擊，咁見到形勢唔對路而目標已經基本上達成，唔閃等幾時? 聽日後日再嚟過啦，最緊要係齊上齊落!<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21e0b50854aa18e7156600e2abc6085dd2a383c","tid":1457182,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁咪返去 變返多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec5eba883c7a3036414b7a29be11ec4ca70f0c","tid":1457182,"uid":238027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21e0b50854aa18e7156600e2abc6085dd2a383c","tid":1457182,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:22:53.000Z","msg":"咁咪返去 變返多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"你hold到長期咁多人先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚呢凌晨呢<br />\n咁多人陪你無間斷長期抗爭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8412efb4e11b1021001b765829f2a8a875648055","tid":1457182,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ec5eba883c7a3036414b7a29be11ec4ca70f0c","tid":1457182,"uid":238027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21e0b50854aa18e7156600e2abc6085dd2a383c","tid":1457182,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit